    "name": "Mapinguari",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "The mapinguari is a creature of legend, a beast many claim to have seen, though few who actually encounter one live to tell their story. A mapinguari patrols a territory so large that some believe each claims an entire jungle as its own. However, those more familiar with the legends know that a mapinguari\u2019s territory is greatly limited by lakes, rivers, and other bodies of water. <br/><br/>A mapinguari stands approximately 20 feet tall and weighs 15,000 pounds."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>This immense, green creature stands on two thick legs, glaring with a single massive eye as it displays knifelike talons.</i>",
